I was going to buy another GBC emulator, which had more graphic options (GBC.emu by Robert). However, that emulator had an unsatisfying UI. For this emulator, the UI is 100% satisfying. It lets you know which directional button you're pressing, Quick Save/Quick Load double tap implementation is amazing, Turbo Buttons, Fast Forward, etc. Not to mention, it's based on Gambatte, which is known for high emulation compatibility. I will take the sacrifice on graphics options for this amazing UI.

replyContent: Since you chose not to reply to our email, we cannot help you any further. Anyway, the Pro and the Lite versions are very same when it comes to file searching, so it seems impossible that you wouldn't see some games in the Pro app... Try tapping on "Search for ROMs" in the menu to refresh the game list.
